{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_PhoenixPuff}}
'''A_PhoenixPuff'''<br />
(no parameters)

Spawns two {{Class|PhoenixPuff}} actors, and sends them straight to the left and the right of the calling actor, with a horizontal speed of 1.3 and no vertical speed. In Heretic, the function also called [[A_SeekerMissile]] with a threshold of 5° and a maximum angle of 10°, however the calling actor itself was never given a tracer to follow.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|PhoenixFX1}} and derived classes.

